UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1446
1 AN ACT relating to on-farm animal health.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 SECTION 1. A NEW SECTION OF KRS CHAPTER 257 IS CREATED TO
4 READ AS FOLLOWS:
5 Notwithstanding any other provision of law to the contrary, the determination and
6 implementation of any on-farm animal health care or animal health production
7 practice shall be made solely by a farmer and his or her veterinarian, as defined in
8 KRS 321.181, pursuant to the veterinarian-client-patient relationship, as defined in
9 KRS 321.181.
